                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As seen at &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/driftx/cassandra/1551/workflows/be2ca359-49d7-4fb3-959d-454656f48d79/jobs/80604/tests&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/driftx/cassandra/1551/workflows/be2ca359-49d7-4fb3-959d-454656f48d79/jobs/80604/tests&lt;/a&gt; :&lt;/p&gt;

